cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the bias catalog, please cite as below."
type: software
title: "FVB Reference-Genome Mapping Bias RNA-seq Analysis Pipeline"
abstract: >
  Analysis code and figure-generation scripts for systematic characterisation of
  SNP-mediated reference-genome mapping bias in FVB mouse RNA-seq experiments,
  including a 32-gene bias catalog and three-arm pipeline (naive / WASP / FVB personalised reference).
authors:
